Package: schrodinger
Type: Package
Title: Find the eigenvalues and eigenfunctions of the one-dimensional Schrodinger problem
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Robert Carcassés Quevedo
Maintainer: Robert Carcassés Quevedo <carcasses@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows to solve one dimensional quantum mechanic problems by using two different algorithms: Numerov and a Chebyshev polynomial based one.
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.5)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
